  "body": "Discovered while reproducing https://github.com/coredns/coredns/issues/2257\r\n\r\n```\r\n# ... dig output ...\r\n;; Query time: 1 msec\r\n;; SERVER: ::1#1053(::1)\r\n;; WHEN: Thu Nov 01 14:15:59 CET 2018\r\n;; MSG SIZE  rcvd: 4119\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n[::1]:51981 - [01/Nov/2018:14:15:59 +0100] 263 \"SRV IN http.web.stnn.rocket.srv.db.s-cloud.net. udp 81 false 4096\" NOERROR qr,tc,rd,ra 6943 0.001206116s\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt appears that dig reports the msg size as 4119, but the logging plugin says it is 6943.\r\n\r\nI haven't checked, but this response bytes reported in the prometheus plugin could also be wrong.",
